   "source": [
    "#| title: \"Global Income Inequality Dashboard\"\n",
    "#| subtitle: \"Market Income vs. Disposable Income Gini Coefficients\"\n",
    "#| layout: columns\n",
    "#| column: body\n",
    "#| fig-width: 12\n",
    "#| fig-height: 8\n",
    "\n",
    "# Import libraries\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import plotly.express as px\n",
    "import plotly.graph_objects as go\n",
    "from plotly.subplots import make_subplots\n",
    "import ipywidgets as widgets\n",
    "from IPython.display import display\n",
    "\n",
    "# Load your data\n",
    "df = pd.read_csv('https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rfordatascience/tidytuesday/main/data/2025/2025-08-05/income_inequality_processed.csv')\n",
    "# Rename columns for clarity\n",
    "df = df.rename(columns={\n",
    "    'Entity': 'Country',\n",
    "    'gini_mi_eq': 'Market_Income_Gini',\n",
    "    'gini_dhi_eq': 'Disposable_Income_Gini'\n",
    "})\n",
    "\n",
    "# Calculate redistribution effect\n",
    "df['Redistribution_Effect'] = df['Market_Income_Gini'] - df['Disposable_Income_Gini']"
   ]
  },

   "source": [
    "#| column: screen-right\n",
    "#| panel: sidebar\n",
    "\n",
    "# Create interactive widgets\n",
    "print(\"## Data Overview\")\n",
    "print(f\"Dataset shape: {df.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Years covered: {df['Year'].min()} to {df['Year'].max()}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Countries: {df['Country'].nunique()}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Create interactive widgets\n",
    "countries = widgets.SelectMultiple(\n",
    "    options=df['Country'].unique(),\n",
    "    value=['Australia', 'United States', 'Germany', 'Sweden', 'Brazil'],\n",
    "    description='Countries:',\n",
    "    disabled=False\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "year_range = widgets.IntRangeSlider(\n",
    "    value=[1990, 2020],\n",
    "    min=df['Year'].min(),\n",
    "    max=df['Year'].max(),\n",
    "    step=1,\n",
    "    description='Year Range:',\n",
    "    disabled=False\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "gini_type = widgets.RadioButtons(\n",
    "    options=[\"Market Income\", \"Disposable Income\", \"Both\"],\n",
    "    value=\"Both\",\n",
    "    description='Gini Type:',\n",
    "    disabled=False\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "display(countries)\n",
    "display(year_range)\n",
    "display(gini_type)"
   ]
  },

    "#| column: screen-inset\n",
    "#| panel: fill\n",
    "\n",
    "# Time series of Gini coefficients\n",
    "filtered_df = df[\n",
    "    (df['Country'].isin(countries.value)) & \n",
    "    (df['Year'] >= year_range.value[0]) & \n",
    "    (df['Year'] <= year_range.value[1])\n",
    "]\n",
    "\n",
    "if gini_type.value == \"Both\":\n",
    "    fig1 = px.line(filtered_df, \n",
    "                  x='Year', y=['Market_Income_Gini', 'Disposable_Income_Gini'],\n",
    "                  color='Country',\n",
    "                  title='Income Inequality Trends',\n",
    "                  labels={'value': 'Gini Coefficient', 'variable': 'Type'})\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    column = 'Market_Income_Gini' if gini_type.value == \"Market Income\" else 'Disposable_Income_Gini'\n",
    "    fig1 = px.line(filtered_df, \n",
    "                  x='Year', y=column,\n",
    "                  color='Country',\n",
    "                  title=f'{gini_type.value} Inequality Trends')\n",
    "    \n",
    "fig1.show()"
   ]

    "#| column: screen-inset\n",

    "\n",
    "# World map visualization (latest year)\n",
    "latest_year = df['Year'].max()\n",
    "map_df = df[df['Year'] == latest_year]\n",
    "\n",
    "fig4 = px.choropleth(map_df,\n",
    "                    locations=\"Code\",\n",
    "                    color=\"Disposable_Income_Gini\",\n",
    "                    hover_name=\"Country\",\n",
    "                    hover_data=[\"Market_Income_Gini\", \"Disposable_Income_Gini\"],\n",
    "                    color_continuous_scale=px.colors.sequential.Plasma,\n",
    "                    title=f\"Global Income Inequality (Disposable Income, {latest_year})\")\n",
    "fig4.show()"
   ]
